==English==
===Etymology===
Named after English physician ''[[w:James_Parkinson|James Parkinson]]'' (1755-1824).

===Noun phrase===
'''Parkinson’s [[disease]]'''

#A chronic [[neurological]] [[disorder]] resulting in lack of control over movement; poor balance and coordination; and similar symptoms.

